## Environment Variables Template for Vercel Deployment

## AI & Embeddings
GROQ_API_KEY=your_groq_api_key_here
EMBEDDING_API_KEY=your_huggingface_api_key_here

## App URL (update with your Vercel deployment URL)
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=https://your-app.vercel.app

## Supabase (Required for Vercel)
SUPABASE_URL=your_supabase_project_url
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=your_supabase_service_role_key

## MySQL Configuration
## For Vercel deployment, MySQL will work if:
## 1. Your RDS security group allows Vercel's IP ranges (76.76.21.0/24)
## 2. OR you don't set these variables and the app will use Supabase cache instead
MYSQL_HOST=your_mysql_host_here
MYSQL_PORT=3306
MYSQL_USER=your_mysql_user
MYSQL_PASSWORD=your_mysql_password
MYSQL_DATABASE=your_database_name
